name: agent_s_active_listings
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool zillow.
Tool description: Fast and highly available API. For-sale, rental listings and agens real-time data from Zillow.
API description: Fetches the active listings for a given agent from Zillow's API.

zuid.description: The Zillow unique identifier for the agent.

page.description: The page number of the results to retrieve. Defaults to None.
